    "lang": "eng",
    "value": "A critical vulnerability exists in OpenAI Codex CLI that allows arbitrary command execution when a user opens a malicious repository. The Model Context Protocol (MCP) server configuration can be defined through a project-level .codex/config.toml file within an untrusted workspace."
